attributes.Long form description: The student assembles a rolling cart. First, he assembles the bars side. At the beginning he doubts how they should be assembled, and the instructor directs him. Then he forms the base frame. He also starts it by putting it wrong and then the instructor explains to him what is wrong and tells him how to put it and he can put it. He puts the bottom tray, puts the bracket on each side and screws them, and then follows with the middle tray and does the same with the top tray and he also puts the bracket on each side and screws them. Finally he puts the tires and assembles the rolling cart.
